definition: of plants or animals originating in a part of the world other than where they are growing
details:
adjective
- of plants or animals originating in a part of the world other than where they are growing
- of persons born in another area or country than that lived in
= example: of persons born in another area or country than that lived in
= synonyms: foreign-born
- not being or composed of aborigines
= example: not being or composed of aborigines
